# Basic Information Specifications

TikTok for Developers requires you to provide basic information about your app. Once submitted, we will review this information for compliance with our policies.

Submission and approval of your app's basic information is mandatory for app publication.

## Prerequisite

You must have an app that represents your mini drama registered under an organization on the Developer Portal.

## Fill out your app's basic information

Click the **Basic information** tab on your app page to find the requested information.

![](https://sf16-sg.tiktokcdn.com/obj/tiktok-open-platform-sg/ttop_doc_images/2cf2a4dc905b8907c8d7971c4ce5f0a2)

### App information

Fill out your app's information. You must comply with [TikTok's community guidelines](https://www.tiktok.com/community-guidelines/en), ensuring that your app information does not contain non-compliant content. Apps that do not meet our safety baseline will not pass moderation.

**Field**

**Requirements**

App icon

Your app icon displayed to users:

*   PNG, JPEG, JPG, BMP
*   600 x 600 px, up to 6MB
*   Must not contain rounded corners, watermarks, or QR codes
*   Must not infringe IP or contain illegal content
*   Must be a clear image
*   Must not contain any sensitive or inappropriate content
*   Must not be easily confused with another well-known brand icon
*   Must be consistent with the app name or brand

App name

Your app name displayed to users:

*   Must not exceed 50 characters
*   Should be appropriate and not contain any sensitive terminology

*   _Examples: Any adult content, like lottery, gambling, abortion, violence, drugs, and any potentially negative or harmful content, like conspiracy theories, terrorism, and more_

*   Should not be, include, or be attempting to copy the name of other well-known apps

*   _Examples: TikTok, Tik Tok, T1kTok, and use of a few characters together with Tik/Tok_

*   Must match the description

Description

A brief explanation of what your mini drama does and how it works, displayed to users

*   Must not exceed 500 characters.
*   Must be compliant with the [TikTok Community Guidelines](https://www.tiktok.com/community-guidelines/en/) and [TikTok Developer Terms of Service](https://www.tiktok.com/legal/tik-tok-developer-terms-of-service)

### Terms & Privacy

TikTok for Developers requires you to provide URLs for your official Terms of Service and Privacy Policy. These will be displayed on your mini drama's loading page.

*   **Terms of Service URL**: Your Terms of Service address that will be displayed to users for access.
*   **Privacy Policy URL**: Your Privacy Policy address that will be displayed to users for access.
*   **Service domains**: The domains that your platform owns. Extract the domains from our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy URLs and paste them here.

### Release regions

Select where you will launch your mini drama. Some regions may have specific requirements.

**Region**

**Specific requirements**

Brazil, Indonesia, Japan, Malaysia, Philippines, Saudi Arabia, Thailand, Turkey

None



United States

Approval from TikTok to launch in the US. Learn more about [requesting approval for US launch](/doc/launch-your-app-to-us-users-minigames).

